headline: Can SRS and GMS Cement Home Depot's Hold on the Pro Market?
summary: HD's strategic acquisitions of SRS and GMS strengthen contractor relationships, expanding specialty offerings and building a full-service Pro ecosystem.

headline: Assessing Lowe's Stock Value After Recent Price Swings and Earnings Trends
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Lowe's Companies stock right now? You are not alone. There are plenty of investors trying to decide whether recent price swings are the start of something big, a bump in the road, or a new normal for the home improvement giant. Lowe's shares closed at $245.27 most recently, and while they are up 1.9% over the past week, the stock has lost 7.5% in the last month and is down 0.7% so far this year.
